channel.title: [508] F2P/P2P Server Development With Grand Exchange Added[508]
channel.description:
[center]I've recently been working on a project, and decided to release what I've developed so far. This 508 Project is for P2P Worlds and F2P worlds on a 508. Members Items will only be available on a P2P World, and Non-Members Items will only be available on a F2P world. If you log-in using a Member world, with F2P items, they will not be visible, if you log-in to a Non-Member world, with P2P items, they will also not be visible.[/center]
[center][size=15pt][u][i][b]This is the World Select Screen so far.[/b][/i][/u][/size] [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn131/Evoze/Worlds.jpg[/img]
[center][size=15pt][b][i][u]Grand Exchange[/u][/i][/b][/size][/center] [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn131/Evoze/GrandExchange.jpg[/img]
[center][u][i][b][size=15pt]Clan Chat[/size][/b][/i][/u][/center] [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn131/Evoze/ClanChat.jpg[/img] ----------------- [u][i][b][size=15pt]Now, for a Class you can pick.[/size][/b][/i][/u] 1 - F2P Rune/2H 2 - F2P Rune Scimi/Shield 3 - P2P Bandos/Whip/DFS 4 - P2P Bandos/AGS/2H
[size=15pt][u][i][b]Classes.[/b][/i][/u][/size] [IMG]http://i303.photobucket.com/albums/nn131/Evoze/Classes-1.jpg[/img]
This is all I have so far, as I'm still working on improving it. For the F2P Rune/2h i decided to keep it the old way you held it better, Cause it looked cooler. ---------------- [size=15pt][u][i][b]Things I'm currently working on:[/b][/i][/u][/size] -PVP F2P/P2P -Grand Exchange F2P/P2P -Trading F2P/P2P
Thanks, I'll update everytime I get farther. [/center]
